com a Dra. Kepner.

63
00:03:14,001 --> 00:03:16,449
Laurel Pinson...

64
00:03:16,450 --> 00:03:19,074
Minha.

65
00:03:19,075 --> 00:03:23,085
Laurel, com o Dr. Karev.

66
00:03:23,086 --> 00:03:26,588
Edward Taylor,
